# Walkthrough — GoLive Phase 11: Subscriptions & Social

## Summary
Completed the social loop with Subscription feeds and interactive comments.

---

## Changes Made

### 1. Subscriptions System
- **Database**: New `subscriptions` table tracking follower relationships.
- **Button**: [SubscribeButton](file:///C:/GoLive/components/SubscribeButton.tsx#16-128) component handles toggling state and auth checks. Added to Watch Page.
- **Feed Page**: `/subscriptions` displays a personalized grid of videos from channels the user follows.

### 2. Comments Refactor
- **Component**: Extracted [CommentSection](file:///C:/GoLive/components/CommentSection.tsx#24-198) for reusability and cleaner code.
- **Realtime**: Subscribes to Supabase changes to show new comments instantly.
- **Deletion**: Users can now delete their own comments.

### 3. Watch Page Cleanup
- Removed legacy inline code, now uses clean components.
- Integrated [SubscribeButton](file:///C:/GoLive/components/SubscribeButton.tsx#16-128) next to channel info.

## Verification
- **Build**: Passed.
- **Manual Test**: Subscribe button toggles correctly. Feed page filters videos by subscription. Comments post and delete instantly.
